        {
          "renderType": "rich-text",
          "tag": "h2",
          "content": "What is Fortis Group?"
        },
        {
          "renderType": "rich-text",
          "tag": "p",
          "content": "Fortis Group is a general contracting company with over 40 years of experience in the construction industry. They work in a variety of sectors with clients spanning institutional, commercial, industrial, recreational and residential industries. They are known for their experience, reputation and innovation in communities they operate in."
        }
