            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "We applied this new look and feel to other pages reusing elements and patterns where suitable to create a cohesive and consistent look. The text blocks overlapping images component and variants of it were used across project, team and news pages. This component in particular was designed to be flexible to accommodate different amounts and types of information."
