              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "With individual project pages, we were working with a blank canvas as their existing site didn't have any. Based on what we saw on competitor sites and the importance of displaying the quality of their work we opted for a simple easy-to-follow layout with key information like budget, size, sector, client and project description at the top and images of the final outcome below."
