              "content": "We took inspiration in some aspects of content development and visual design from competitor sites, but differentiating Fortis Group from their competitors was also important. Animations were a great way to achieve this. They also help add to the presentation of their work and team and help create a sleek and impressive feel overall. Below are samples of animations at work from a unique page loader to page transitions to reveals on scroll."
